<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>ema523_01_IH_0007</title>

    <!-- 공통 js-->
    <script src="../../common_contents/common/js/app.js"></script>
    <script src="../../common_practice/common/js/solve_area_act.js"></script>

    <!-- 공통 css-->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_contents/common/css/app.css" />

    <!-- 개별 -->
    <script src="./../../common_practice/js/ema523_01_ih_0001.js"></script>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_practice/common/css/app.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_practice/css/ema523_01.css" />
  </head>

  <body>
    <div id="app_wrap" class="ema523_01_ih_0001">
      <section class="title flex_wrap">
        <h2 lang="y">
          <span class="recap" lang="y">이전에 <span>배웠어요</span></span>
          <span class="title_text" lang="y">『수학 4-1』 평면도형 뒤집기, 평면도형 돌리기</span>
        </h2>
      </section>
      <section class="title type2">
        <h2 data-head="1">
          <span lang="y">도형을 오른쪽으로 뒤집었을 때의 도형과 시계 반대 방향으로 180° 만큼 돌렸을 때의 도형을 각각 그려 보세요.</span>
        </h2>
      </section>

      <section class="contents">
        <div class="flex">
          <div class="quiz_area">
            <div class="image image1">
              <img src="../../common_practice/img/EMA523_01_IH/0001_01.svg" alt="사다리꼴" />
            </div>
            <div class="image image2">
              <img src="../../common_practice/img/EMA523_01_IH/0001_02.svg" alt="오른쪽으로 뒤집기" />
            </div>
            <div class="line_area" id="lineArea1"></div>
            <div class="line_area" id="lineArea2"></div>
            <div class="drawline_grid">
              <div class="drawing_grid_area" id="drawingArea1" data-grid-size="60" data-answer-single='[[{"x":0,"y":0},{"x":0,"y":240},{"x":240,"y":240},{"x":240,"y":180}]]'>
                <svg class="line_canvas"></svg>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="quiz_area">
            <div class="image image3">
              <img src="../../common_practice/img/EMA523_01_IH/0001_01.svg" alt="사다리꼴" />
            </div>
            <div class="image image4">
              <img src="../../common_practice/img/EMA523_01_IH/0001_03.svg" alt="시계 반대 방향으로 180도 만큼 돌리기" />
            </div>
            <div class="line_area" id="lineArea3"></div>
            <div class="line_area" id="lineArea4"></div>
            <div class="drawline_grid">
              <div class="drawing_grid_area" id="drawingArea2" data-grid-size="60" data-answer-single='[[{"x":0,"y":0},{"x":0,"y":240},{"x":240,"y":60},{"x":240,"y":0}]]'>
                <svg class="line_canvas"></svg>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- 해설 -->
        <div class="solve_area">
          <div class="inner_solve">
            <div class="flex">
              <strong class="tit_solve" lang="y">해설</strong>
              <div class="conts_solve">
                <p lang="y" class="text_bullet">도형을 오른쪽으로 뒤집으면 도형의 왼쪽과 오른쪽이 서로 바뀝니다.</p>
                <p lang="y" class="text_bullet">도형을 시계 반대 방향으로 180°만큼 돌리면 도형의 위쪽 부분이 아래쪽으로 이동합니다.</p>

                <p lang="y" class="text_label">
                  <span class="label reference">참고</span>
                  도형을 뒤집거나 돌리면 도형의 방향만 바뀌고 모양은 변하지 않습니다.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="buttons_solve"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="btn_area">
          <button class="btnReset">리셋</button>
          <button class="btnCheck">확인</button>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
